
To Do List Application

A responsive and interactive task management app built with HTML5, Tailwind CSS, and JavaScript. It allows users to add, complete, and delete tasks with persistent data storage using localStorage.
Features

### Core Features
- Add Tasks
- Mark Complete/Incomplete
- Delete Tasks
- Persistent Storage with localStorage

### Optional Enhancements (Coming Soon)
- Inline Task Editing
- Dark Mode Toggle
- Priority Levels
- Task Categories
- Search & Filtering

### Tecnologies Used

- HTML5 (Semantic Structure)
- Tailwind CSS (Responsive Design)
- JavaScript (DOM Manipulation & Event Handling)
- LocalStorage (Data Persistence)

